            "title": "What types of fragrance does Pacifica Beauty offer?",
            "answer": "<p>Pacifica Beauty offers a wide range of fragrance formats including <strong>perfume, hair perfume, and hair & body mists</strong>. Explore the full <a href=\"/collections/perfume\" title=\"Vegan Perfume & Fragrance\">fragrance collection</a> featuring iconic scents like <a href=\"/products/indian-coconut-nectar-spray-perfume-1\" title=\"Indian Coconut Nectar Spray Perfume\">Indian Coconut Nectar</a> and <a href=\"/collections/tahitian-gardenia-legacy-scent\" title=\"Tahitian Gardenia Legacy Scent\">Tahitian Gardenia</a> designed for everyday wear, layering, and personal expression. </p>"
          }
        },
        "question_ThWBkG": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is the difference between perfume, hair perfume, and body mist?",
            "answer": "<p>Perfume is typically more concentrated and designed for longer wear on skin, while hair perfume is formulated to lightly scent the hair without heaviness. Hair and body mists offer a lighter, more refreshing fragrance experience that can be worn on both skin and hair throughout the day.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_tnmWpC": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What are mood-boosting scents?",
            "answer": "<p>Pacifica Beauty fragrance is inspired by mood-boosting scent profiles designed to uplift, energise, or calm the senses. These fragrances are created to support emotional wellbeing through carefully crafted scent combinations and aromatic inspiration.</p>"
