        "question_48pXCf": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is Pacifica Beauty fragrance based on aromatherapy?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Fragrance at Pacifica Beauty is deeply rooted in aromatherapy. Founder Brook Harvey Taylor is a certified aromatherapist, and this foundation influences how scents are developed—focusing on emotional connection, balance, and sensory experience.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_VcdAX9": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I layer perfume, hair perfume, and body mist?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, layering fragrance is encouraged. You can combine perfume with hair perfume or a hair and body mist to build a personalised scent experience that evolves throughout the day. Try pairing <a href=\"/products/vanilla-whip-spray-perfume\" title=\"Vanilla Whip Eau de Parfum\">Vanilla Whip</a> Perfume with a complementary body mist and hair perfume for a longer-lasting scent story.</p>"
          }
        },
