          "settings": {
            "title": "Are Pacifica Beauty fragrances vegan and cruelty-free?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, all fragrances from Pacifica Beauty are vegan and cruelty-free, designed to deliver beautiful scent experiences while aligning with ethical beauty values.</p>"
